window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In the long, hot summer of 1976 Adam, Rufus, Shiva, Vivien and Zosie are camping at Wyvis Hall. They don’t ask why they are there or how they are to live; they simply scavenge, steal and sell the family heirlooms.</p> <p>Ten years later, the bodies of a woman and child are discovered in the Hall’s animal cemetery. But which woman? And whose child?</p>"; 
